A Comment on Hepatitis B & C, nosocomial - USA (03): (OH)
---------------------------------------------------------
Infection chains for HCV and active HBV infection can be made likely
or unlikely by sequencing the variable parts of the genome and
comparing the results. Infection (not disease, as you may be infected
without disease) status of the dentist may not be that important as
transmission from one infected patient to subsequently treated
patients may be possible as well.

--
